Download, python:
Version 3.7.9, more bigger not run in OS like windows 7
https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.7.9/python-3.7.9-amd64.exe

After that install, two packages
# web framework
pip install flask

# waitress is use to run server in production, if use linux, better options is gunicorn
pip install waitress

# Run server
waitress-serve --listen=*:5000 wsgi:app